                  Angular Features
             ----------------------
    1.Component(Root - AppComponent)

    2.Module(root - AppModule)

    3.Data binding

        3.1. one way binding

            3.1.1 Component To View

                3.1.1.1 String Interpolation/Interpolation({{expresiion}})

                3.1.1.2 Property Binding - [Binding - Target]="Binding-source"

            3.1.2 View to Component

                3.1.2.1 Event Binding - (event) = "function call"

                3.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event - (event) = "function call($event)"

                3.1.2.3 Template Referance variable - (#variable) # with name of variable

        3.2 Two Way Binding

            angular has no ngModule so its imported

            3.2.1 NgModel - (import FormsModules  in app.module.ts),[(ngModel)]='variable-name' this variable can be declared in class]

    4.Dependency Injection 

    5.Services==used to write reused code

    6.Template driven angular Forms

    7.Model driven angular Forms

        7.1 Reactive Forms (ReactiveFormsModule)

            7.1.1 Form Group

            7.1.2 Form Array

            7.1.3 Form Control

    8.Angular Directives

        8.1 Component Directives

        8.2 Structural Directives
            8.2.1 *ngIf="condition"
            8.2.2  *ngFor=
            8.2.3  *ngSwitch
